76561198066942912,Recommended,278910,11586743,"Posted: 7 August, 2014",all,Flixjule,"Creative, original, entertaining, awesome. Interplanetary is a multiplayer turn-based strategy game which is about building up your own planet with cities, and trying to destroy your enemy.The game takes place in a single solar system with two civilized planets that are basically trying to destroy one another. On your own planet you can build cities with power plants and mines to collect resources. You can build defenses to shoot down an enemy incoming missile or a shield over your city to protect it. Also you can build weapons which shoot missiles or lasers to destroy the cities of your enemy. But beware! Have you ever heard of gravity? I bet you do, well you and your enemy are not the only planets floating around in this solar system. All planets have gravity, and it's your job to line up your shots correctly with the influence of gravity to hit your target. Well, these were just the basics...I like this game alot because the concept is so unique, i've never seen a game like this. Unfortunately there are not so many people online. So I reccomend buying this game with a friend so you can play together.Have fun in your own solar system. To the stars, and beyond!"
